org.jbei.ice.lib.entry.model

Class Plasmid

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbei.ice.lib.entry.model.Entry
      • org.jbei.ice.lib.entry.model.Plasmid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IDataModel

    @Entity
@Indexed
public class Plasmid
extends Entry
    Store Plasmid specific fields.

    • backbone: Parent backbone of the plasmid, comma separated.
    • originOfReplication: The origin of replication for this plasmid, comma separated.
    • promoters: Promoters that are on this plasmid, comma separated.
    • circular: True if plasmid is circular.
    • replicatesIn:
    Author:
    Timothy Ham, Zinovii Dmytriv, Hector Plahar

    Serialized Form
